ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"唔係好知點反駁呢個論調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"點解警犬可以用高一級武力<br />\n示威者連拎把遮都唔得"},{"pid":"5ab61a37ac4b7a7c946c0ed3ba441562c7c8f5ae","tid":1315280,"uid":41908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:53:24.000Z","msg":"點解政府收你稅就合法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解你收錢就係收保護費係唔合法？<br />\n<br />\n因為政府有政府嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">責任與義務</span></span>呀<br />\n<br />\n你拎政府同市民做比較簡直on9"},{"pid":"d8a158abc58acdec17856c30442da992e0acebad","tid":1315280,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b80d9aaa2e6e57a5251db835c9d9b8411c99a37","tid":1315280,"uid":280116,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"25d592726a5694dd1cdda47d0a127c313e11889d","tid":1315280,"uid":62746,"like":431,"dislike":3,"score":428,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正做咩遮樣？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"即係暴徒行不正企不正？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"你叫連登仔情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47541568280e1b5a7939762c107448f2904763f","tid":1315280,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea21aa75c518136f205b08c7b8ba8a9025c25cc2","tid":1315280,"uid":280116,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"其實冇得反駁，本身啲人帶口罩就唔合理，自己理虧"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"你老母做雞好合理?"},{"pid":"1fd0de5b004d021f14a1d698f0f418851e09d25f","tid":1315280,"uid":6024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"你執行緊職務呀"},{"pid":"af86b661bdaecfd0ec97df48c2f506079513bc88","tid":1315280,"uid":206617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b80d9aaa2e6e57a5251db835c9d9b8411c99a37","tid":1315280,"uid":280116,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"25d592726a5694dd1cdda47d0a127c313e11889d","tid":1315280,"uid":62746,"like":431,"dislike":3,"score":428,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正做咩遮樣？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"即係暴徒行不正企不正？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"警方有法律賦予既權力去捉啲示威者<br />\n而示威者真正有效控制到警方濫權既能力，只有係透過 number 同拍片影樣進行投訴<br />\n但家下警察遮哂樣，係令到市民限制警權既最後一道防線都冇埋<br />\n<br />\n作為一個法治社會，唔應只講求用法律管治人民，咁係單純以法治港，唔係法治，係法制<br />\n<br />\n法治更講求對權力機關既約束。一班負責執法既警察，無視警察通例，甚至公然隱藏自己既警察編號既同時，又利用法律賦予佢地既權力，呢個先係真正既法治崩壞<br />\n<br />\n因為示威者違法，仲有警察去搜。但警察違法，點處理？&ldquo;按正常程序&rdquo;？"},{"pid":"412f8f341bcc3818d8a23a97d22cb9f1f7da8c20","tid":1315280,"uid":280116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c47541568280e1b5a7939762c107448f2904763f","tid":1315280,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea21aa75c518136f205b08c7b8ba8a9025c25cc2","tid":1315280,"uid":280116,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"其實冇得反駁，本身啲人帶口罩就唔合理，自己理虧"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"你老母做雞好合理?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"冇文化真係好恐怖，幾時都話要讀多啲書，鬧人起碼唔會詞窮先竹"},{"pid":"35f00d15d23d072908335c51a162efdcf56a0af7","tid":1315280,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:00:41.000Z","msg":"你唔收人工，俾埋一樣嘅工具我，咁咪得囉"},{"pid":"5d135f657e8ae6d84346a050504b05ac21c5e59a","tid":1315280,"uid":47524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"咁俾威者用掍用椒同用槍ok??"},{"pid":"fb3267c91885a5b0bede2222cc5f08f63db81235","tid":1315280,"uid":280116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c47541568280e1b5a7939762c107448f2904763f","tid":1315280,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea21aa75c518136f205b08c7b8ba8a9025c25cc2","tid":1315280,"uid":280116,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":4